<div class="language-html line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="html"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 输入标签名 h1 按tab键或Enter键自动补齐 --></span></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>HTML快捷输入练习<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
